physical:
Deadlift
A) Warm up, then take 15:00 minutes build to a comfortable heavy set of 5.
Rest 2:00 between working sets.

B) Post-work: 3×15 Hip Thrusts.
Rest 1:00.

→ Track your effort — every day counts. Log it in the OMNIFIT app.
neurological: Stand on one leg for 45 seconds each side. Keep balance steady.
cognitive: Say one useful thing you will finish today. Speak it clearly.
emotional: Breathe in through your nose for 4 sec, out through your mouth for 4. Do 5 rounds.
lifestyle: Drink half a bottle of water before your morning coffee.

physical:

10 Neutral-Grip Pull-ups
20 Push-ups.

Rest as needed

→ Track your effort — every day counts. Log it in the OMNIFIT app.

physical:

-Sit-Ups
-Walking Lunges
-Bear Crawl or Wall Walk

→ Track your effort — every day counts. Log it in the OMNIFIT app.

physical:
18:00 EMOM
Work 30s / Rest 30s — Jump Rope or March in Place.
Keep breathing easy-nasal.

→ Track your effort — every day counts. Log it in the OMNIFIT app.
neurological: Step up and down a stair 10 times. Use whole foot.
cognitive: Think of one thing that made you smile today.
emotional: Smile and take one deep breath. Let shoulders drop.
lifestyle: Add one colorful fruit or vegetable to a meal.

physical:
45:00 Easy Walk (Zone 2).
Optional: light backpack.
Breathe through the nose.

→ Track your effort — every day counts. Log it in the OMNIFIT app.

emotional: Walk slowly for 5 minutes. Feel calm before you move on.
lifestyle: Sit outside for 5 minutes without your phone.

Burpees
-Move smooth; keep reps steady.

→ Track your effort — every day counts. Log it in the OMNIFIT app.

physical:

6 Goblet Lunges (alternating legs)
3 Lateral Burpees Over
1 Strict Pull-up
Rest 1:1; (If a round took 0:30s - Rest 0:30s)

4 sets × 20 m Bottom-Up Carry / arm.
Build to Challenging Load
Rest as needed

emotional: Lie down, breathe slow, and relax for 2 minutes.
lifestyle: Drink a glass of water before each meal today.
